WARNING: This game isn't an educational piece of software. This is a horror game that will probably scare the living hell out of your child if he or she plays this. However, if your child does like horror games, let them play it, I honestly don't care.
(P.S. This is a fangame of Dave's Fun Algebra Class.)

Click to continue.
Use the arrow keys to move around and stuff. There is no inventory in this game; just run away from Dave and dodge the obstacles.
